Steps to setup:
Install linux which supports mmap (for dsnoop) (https://blog.georgmill.de/2015/04/06/update-rt-kernel-for-cirrus-logicwolfson-audio-card/)
Install icecast
Install darkice
pip install --upgrade  pyalsaaudio 

add /etc/asound.conf file
add /etc/darkice.cfg file
icecast error logs at /var/log/icecast2/

